data.description: Welcome Home to this Cozy Ranch!  Large Front porch is great for entertaining.  Back Yard has been completely upgraded with steps to lower level part of the yard, firepit, and chain link fence! Inside you will find such a warm welcoming space.  You'll feel that very feeling upon entering into the living room that flows to the eat-in kitchen. Kitchen features dishwasher, refrigerator, smart microwave, and stove which are all a part of the 21 sunset package.  Washer and Dryer downstairs also are included! Speaking of downstairs the current owners have created a cute children's playroom with padded flooring. Perfect if you need the same or if you needed an additional room for perhaps an office, bonus room etc. Basement with additional room possibilities also features a half bath and a walk-out door to back yard. Chicken coop included, chickens are not (sorry).  After a fun day in the backyard or in the playroom take a load off in your jetted tub...ahh sounds lovely doesn't it?  What I love about this house is the rural cozy feel, close proximity to amenities, off street parking, and the fenced in backyard that would be great for gathering with friends and family. Call your favorite agent to set up a showing and see what all this property has to offer for yourself! -Updated to add front porch has been freshly painted and possession (day to get keys) will be the same day the house has officially closed!
